name: Fredrich Nietzsche
quotes: Man is something that should be overcome. What have you done to overcome him? All creatures hitherto have created something beyond themselves: and do you want to be the ebb of this great tide, and return to the animals rather than overcome man?
You must have chaos within you to give birth to a dancing star. You still have chaos within you.
